{"tid":1088864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現在六百萬的樓是上車盤？","createTime":"2019-04-02T11:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T11:49:59.000Z","uid":32213,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc751aa282edfc25e4447b4233f382e2d91c2bc2","tid":1088864,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"記得舊年換樓本來想買六球樓下<br />\n最後發現六球樓下根本冇符合要求嘅<br />\n最終要買六球嘅樓<br />\n都覺得十五十六好似太貴了<br />\n但依家叫到五球樓好似絕無僅有 六球就來變上車盤<br />\n唸當年四球買咗當上住車先當時已經被人話接火捧摸頂心驚驚<br />\n<br />\n有時望住個天花板<br />\n都覺得好迷茫<br />\n到底用六球買咗個空間係咩概念<br />\n好虛無飄渺嘅感覺<br />\n而且仲要供多十幾廿年<br />\n<br />\n一個家係咪就等於一間屋？"},{"pid":"f73908071eac1ccc0f70a3562f2ec6e98c4bd3c6","tid":1088864,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"一個家只等於一個床位"},{"pid":"fa279834cb2ff750f949361838d7c19d61223be2","tid":1088864,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"証明你要求高<br />\n冇其他"},{"pid":"e170527b396efbf8a976c7391c180658ae270dfe","tid":1088864,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"大把樓五球 四球就絕無僅有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bd26c177db342ed0178bffd021cd4015268880","tid":1088864,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:17:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64a42f0f5146488c6e35b085fa41d451ee09dd34","tid":1088864,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e170527b396efbf8a976c7391c180658ae270dfe","tid":1088864,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"大把樓五球 四球就絕無僅有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"三百呎都唔夠嘅五球樓算什麼生活空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}